sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as User
  participant UI as UI
  participant K as Kong
  participant PR as Profile
  participant PL as Plan Pay
  participant AI as AI Service
  participant SQL as SQL
  participant MG as Mongo
  participant GPT as GPT API

  Note over U,GPT: After login JWT on all calls below

  U->>UI: Open dashboard
  UI->>K: GET /api/v1/users/me JWT
  K->>PR: forward
  PR->>SQL: user core
  PR->>MG: user_details
  PR-->>UI: profile JSON

  U->>UI: View plans
  UI->>K: GET /api/v1/plans JWT
  K->>PL: forward
  PL->>SQL: plan catalog
  PL-->>UI: plans

  U->>UI: Static questions
  UI->>K: GET /api/v1/questions JWT
  K->>AI: forward
  AI->>MG: by user group
  AI-->>UI: questions

  U->>UI: Ask AI
  UI->>K: POST /api/v1/ai/chat JWT
  K->>AI: forward
  AI->>GPT: completion
  AI->>MG: optional session
  AI-->>UI: answer
